Install capistrano:

  jruby -S gem install capistrano

Then:

  jruby -S capify .

See the tasks:

  jruby -S bundle exec cap -T

Edit your config/deploy.rb.

Set up the server for capistrano:

  jruby -S bundle exec cap deploy:setup

Check the server is configured for capistrano:

  jruby -S bundle exec cap deploy:setup
